draft.append(Draft("Estacy", "Ulian, Suri", "28/07/2024", "Hồ Quang Dũng","Now that she was a ghost, she finally got to travel a lot, something she didn’t get to do when she was still alive. She no longer had to worry about feeding herself or keeping a roof above her head, what she terribly needed was entertainment. Something she found when she impulsively went to Siargao (airfare was free because nobody even knew she boarded the plane). She was exploring the beaches then when she got tired of the waves (who knew ghosts also got tired?) she went to see the villas. Probably the best decision she had ever done, both as a human and ghost. "))

